Must try handroll bar in NYC! 👏🏼

@handroll_rolling is definitely a must try! They’re located in Midtown South, and they have some of the freshest handrolls! 😍

I tried their bluefin tuna, scallop, spicy salmon, and crispy spicy tuna hand-rolls! You can order one of their hand roll sets and it's actually a pretty good deal! If you eat at the bar, they give you the hand-rolls one by one and if you eat at a table, they wrap the seaweed in plastic so the seaweed stays fresh and crispy! 🤩

We also loved their appetizers, we got their hamachi crudo, salmon sashimi, ebi potato, potato croquette, and shrimp tempura udon! 🍤

Follow @itskimpham for more NYC eats! ✨

📍Midtown, NYC

#midtownnyc #handrollbar #handrolls #sashimi #newyorkfood #nycrestaurants

Unique Latin American food with so much flavor! 😍

On my recent trip to DC I got to check out @sevenreasonsdc! They’re known for their Latin American dishes and tasting menus! We order from their a le carte menu and everything was great! 🤩

Their croquettes were delish, I really enjoyed their short rib as well, it was super tender! And the duck was cooked to perfection! 👌🏼

📍Washington, DC

#washingtondc #dcfoodie #latinamericanfood #dceats #dcrestaurants

Ramen with added health benefits! 🙂‍↕️

@misoyanyc is all about providing quality miso in all their ramen! If you didn’t know, miso is a traditional Japanese health seasoning made from fermented soybeans! It’s good for gut health with probiotic properties, and can potentially boost immunity, boost digestion, lower cholesterol, and support heart health! 💖

You can choose between 3 types of miso broths and each has a different flavor profile and originates from a different region in Japan! They have a Mame miso from Nagoya, Shiro miso from Kyoto, and Kome miso from Hokkaido! We tried the Shiro miso and it was delish! 😋

We also tried their cold ramen which was tangy and refreshing which is perfect for summer! Don’t forget to try their other dishes like their edamame, ebi and vegetable gyoza, sashimi platter, and nori salad! 🥗

There’s so many great options to choose from here and I love how this restaurants focuses on providing health benefits from their food along with amazing taste! 🤩

Follow @itskimpham for more NYC eats! ✨

📍West Village, NYC

#westvillagenyc #ramen #misoramen #japanesemiso #ramenstagram #ramennoodles #ramenlover

One of the coolest cocktail experiences I’ve ever had! 🤩

@barminibyjose is truly a cocktail lab! The set up almost feels like a science experiment with the decor and even the people making the drinks! 🍹

This cocktail bar is created by @barminibyjose which was such a cool experience and the drinks were incredible! They also paid such close attention to detail from the flavors, the ice, the glasses, to the garnish and presentation! 👏🏼

📍Washington, DC

#washingtondc #dcfoodie #washingtondcfood #dcbars #dcbarscene #cocktailsofinstagram

First month into working with an online fitness coach! 🔥

Working with @matt.icanfitness has been so easy! We started off with a consultation call to go over my goals, nutrition, schedule for workouts, and what equipment I have available for my workout! 🏋️‍♀️ 

Then he gives me 3 workouts a week that are all scheduled and available in the @everfit.io app! This app makes it so easy to track my workout duration, reps, weights for each workout, rest time, and even tracks my progress for each workout! 👏🏼

It’s been so nice having my workouts planned for me so I don’t have to think about what types of exercises I should do at the gym. @matt.icanfitness work outs also incorporate a warm up session at the beginning, a small cardio portion, and stretching session at the end! 🏃🏼‍♀️

Now that I’ve been staying more consistent with my workout, I need to focus more on my nutrition to start seeing results! I’ve been tracking all the food I eat every day on @myfitnesspal which gets linked to @everfit.io and Matt can see how I’m doing with my macros and calories 👌🏼

DM me if you’re interested in working with an online coach! I can’t wait to share my fitness journey with all of you! 🤩

#fitness #matticanfitness #onlinefitnesscoach #everfit #myfitnesspal #fitnessjourney

The biggest Latin food festival is here in NJ! 🔥

@ricoricofiesta is happening at @americandream mall at Lot 26 on July 25-27, 2025 from 10am to 10pm! 👏🏼

They’re showcasing 90+ different Latin food vendors and there’s so many food options to choose from! The food is super affordable and food is capped at $15, desserts capped at $12 and drinks capped at $10! 👌🏼

General admission tickets start at $12, VIP tickets for $45 and it’s free admission for kids under 10 years old! VIP tickets include all day entry and re-entry, express check-in line, merch, drinks and more! 🤩

There will be free salsa, bachata, and reggaeton dance workshops and live music performances all weekend long! 💃🏼

Use my promo code “KIMPHAM10” for 10% when purchasing tickets for the event! You won’t want to miss out on this Latin food festival! 🫶🏼

Follow @itskimpham for more NJ eats! ✨

📍American Dream Mall, Lot 26, East Rutherford, NJ

#ricoricofiesta #latinfood #latinfoodfestival #foodfestival #foodies #njfoodies #newjersey

Getting the coolest shots with my new @insta360 x5 camera! 🤩

The accessories you can purchase for your @insta360 are next level! I got their extended selfie stick that extends up to 10 feet long! (Well almost, it’s actually extends to 9.84 feet long to be exact!) you can get cool drone like shots without needing a drone! Great for places that don’t allow drones! 👌🏼

I also got the bullet time selfie stick that swivels when you swing it above your head to get some really cool shots that takes in all the angles and views of your surroundings! 👏🏼

Can’t wait to take this on all my travel adventures! ✈️

#insta360 #insta360bullettime #bullettime #bullettimeeffect #360camera #nyc #insta360x5

Loving all the new Vietnamese spots! 🤩

@ladongnyc is a restaurant that opened up within a year and I’m a fan! They have some really great unique Vietnamese dishes that are presented so beautifully! 💛

They start off by giving you complimentary fish chips with a side of chili oil for dipping! We also got their sugarcane shrimp which is an absolutely must! 🦐

I ordered their bun Bo hue and my fiancé got their pho and both were great! The space is also cutely decorated and felt like a little piece of Vietnam! 🇻🇳

Follow @itskimpham for more NYC eats! ✨

📍Union Square, NYC

#unionsquare #vietnamesefood #nyceats #nycrestaurants #unionsquarenyc #nyc

My fave pho in NYC! 🤩

I don’t even usually like ordering pho so that’s how you know it’s good! @tenten_nyc is serving up a northern style Vietnamese pho and I’m a huge fan! 👏🏼

They use fresh noodles, the broth is very flavorful, and you can get a side of fried long donut or poached egg just like how they serve it in Vietnam! 🇻🇳

They also serve it with pickled garlic, homemade crushed chilli peppers, and lime on the side! 🍋‍🟩

This is such a quick and easy meal, you order right at the front and then they bring the food to you in no time! 👌🏼

Follow @itskimpham for more NYC eats! ✨

📍Chinatown, NYC

#chinatownnyc #vietnamesefood #pho #hanoianfood #hanoi #vietfood #nyceats

The best cronuts in NYC! 🔥

@dominiqueansel is serving up the best cronuts in NYC! Their flavors change every month so you gotta make sure you try it if you’re interested in the flavor for that month because it’ll be gone by next month! 😍

The flavor I tried at the time was an orange blossom and pistachio cream and it was delish!! They also have other amazing pastries, desserts and I seriously just wanted to try them all 💖

Follow @itskimpham for more NYC eats! ✨

📍SoHo, NYC

#soho #newyorkbakery #nycbakery #dominiqueanselbakery #cronut #homeofthecronut

My new fave hand roll bar in NYC! 🤩

@matsunori.handrollbar is serving up some of the most premium hand rolls in NYC! You can find hand rolls with foie gras, uni, a5 wagyu, and caviar! 👏🏼

They actually have a whole separate caviar menu with so many hand rolls topped with caviar! It’s a caviar lovers dream! 😍

I personally really enjoyed the chutoro with mushroom, uni, and the miso black cod with caviar! The portions were huge! Some of the biggest hand rolls I’ve ever had so definitely come here hungry! 😆

Loved the appetizers and the matcha tiramisu here, definitely need to give that a try! 👌🏼

Follow @itskimpham for more NYC eats! ✨

📍Long Island City, Queens
